About Esteban
Introducing Esteban Muñoz, the newly appointed Membership Director at Monarch Country Club. With a solid background in business and country clubs, Esteban brings a wealth of hospitality experience to his role. Having worked in various business and country clubs before joining Monarch, Esteban has a deep understanding of what makes a club truly exceptional. His expertise in hospitality ensures that members will receive top-notch service and experiences during their time at Monarch. Beyond his professional endeavors, Esteban is passionate about golf. You'll often find him on the greens, honing his skills and enjoying the game.
Additionally, he has a creative side as a music producer and DJ, where he channels his artistic talents into producing captivating tunes and cultivating unforgettable experiences. As Esteban settles into his role at Monarch Country Club, members can expect a dedicated and experienced professional at the helm. With his combined passion for hospitality, love for golf, and creative pursuits in music production, Esteban is poised to enhance the club experience for all who walk through the doors of Monarch.

Membership
Monarch Country Club is pleased to offer membership categories for any interest level for those that live inside or outside the gates of the community. Unless otherwise noted, memberships include spouse and dependent children under the age of 24 years of age living at home or attending school on a full-time basis.
Schedule A Tour
Membership Categories
Contact Our Membership Director
Monarch
Full golf Membership entitles Members to unlimited golfing privileges, full access to the private clubhouse including casual dining, six lighted Har-Tru tennis courts, junior-Olympic size swimming pool, fitness center and an array of social and sporting activities. This membership provides preferred tee times and includes greens fees. Cart fees are not included
Regent
Membership entitles Members to unlimited golfing privileges, full access to the private clubhouse including casual dining, six lighted Har-Tru tennis courts, junior-Olympic size swimming pool, fitness center and an array of social and sporting activities. This membership does not include greens fees or cart fees.
Executive Professional
Membership for those ages 44 and under entitles Members to unlimited golfing privileges, full access to the private clubhouse including casual dining, six lighted Har-Tru tennis courts, junior-Olympic size swimming pool, fitness center and an array of social and sporting activities. This membership includes greens fees with cart fees required.
Executive Professional Intermediate
Membership for those ages 45-55 entitles Members to unlimited golfing privileges, full access to the private clubhouse including casual dining, six lighted Har-Tru tennis courts, junior-Olympic size swimming pool, fitness center and an array of social and sporting activities. This membership includes greens fees with cart fees required.
Lifestyle | Social / Fitness / Tennis
Social membership entitles Members full access to the private clubhouse including casual dining, junior-Olympic size swimming pool, fitness center, tennis, and an array of social activities.
The Invited Advantage
In addition to our portfolio of owned or operated golf and country clubs, city clubs and stadium clubs, our network includes alliance clubs and special offerings at more than 1,000 hotels, resorts and entertainment venues.
